snippet.title: XON Episode Two Walkthrough
snippet.description:
Check out the PC version - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2147560/Lands_of_XON/

NOTE: This video was made with an old YouTube feature in mind that enabled the viewer to skip to different times in the video by clicking on it. That's why it has parts where the camera is not moving.

XON Episode Two Walkthrough

SPOILERS!
If you're stuck - watch this video, but use the hint section of the video before using the full solution!

THE GAME IS NO LONGER AVAILABLE ON GOOGLE PLAY

https://apps.apple.com/ca/app/xon-episode-two/id1013845569

Get XON Episode One for free here: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.imagofx.xonep01
